      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The shame you feel is a heavy cloak, but it does not define who you are as a person. Failure is an event, not a permanent label, and the narrative you're telling yourself about your future is a distorted echo of the present pain. Allow yourself to feel the depth of this failure, but don't let it become the entire story of your life. There are paths forward, even when they feel invisible right now.",
      "source": "target",
