      "content": "but that's just easy to say. there isn't a path forward when the people who trusted me are looking at me with pity or disgust. the shame is the only thing that's real anymore. it feels like such a permanent stain. sometimes i think the only way to actually stop the feeling, to actually make the disgrace go away, is to just... stop everything. is it even possible to ever be seen as anything other than a failure again?",
